Git Bash Note (Important)

In Git Bash, do NOT use /p:... (it can break MSBuild).
Use -p: instead:

dotnet publish ./CableGlandPlanner.csproj -c Release -r win-x64 --self-contained true \
  -p:PublishSingleFile=true -p:DebugType=None -p:DebugSymbols=false \
  -o publish_signed

